---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Articles
description: Articles on turning photography and creative skills into digital products, color grading, and building an online business as an artist.
permalink: /articles/
---
<div class="wrap">
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 32px;">
    <h1>Articles</h1>
    <p>Everything I have learned about selling knowledge as a photographer, written down so you can skip the years of trial and error.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="post-list">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <a class="post-card" href="{{ post.url }}">
        <div class="post-meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }} &middot; {{ post.templateContent | readingTime }} min read</div>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description or (post.templateContent | excerpt) }}</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
